name: r-rcmdrmisc
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2.7-2" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-rcmdrmisc
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/RcmdrMisc_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/RcmdrMisc/RcmdrMisc_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 838fc795127ba6b2a4fd6dac1dd58fbccd418299252c659950427fd3aecdbb64

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-hmisc >=4.1_0
    - r-mass
    - r-abind
    - r-car >=3.0_0
    - r-colorspace
    - r-e1071
    - r-foreign
    - r-haven
    - r-nortest
    - r-readstata13
    - r-readxl
    - r-sandwich
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-hmisc >=4.1_0
    - r-mass
    - r-abind
    - r-car >=3.0_0
    - r-colorspace
    - r-e1071
    - r-foreign
    - r-haven
    - r-nortest
    - r-readstata13
    - r-readxl
    - r-sandwich

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('RcmdrMisc')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('RcmdrMisc')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://www.r-project.org, http://socserv.socsci.mcmaster.ca/jfox/
  license: GPL-2
  summary: Various statistical, graphics, and data-management functions used by the Rcmdr package in the R Commander GUI for R.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r

# Package: RcmdrMisc
# Version: 2.7-0
# Date: 2019-12-24
# Title: R Commander Miscellaneous Functions
# Authors@R: c(person("John", "Fox", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "jfox@mcmaster.ca"), person("Robert", "Muenchen", role = "ctb"), person("Dan", "Putler", role = "ctb") )
# Depends: R (>= 3.5.0), utils, car (>= 3.0-0), sandwich
